  "texts": [
    "4 We measure size by simply counting the number of task components.",
    "Variety: Diversity of different task components is considered as the dimension of Variety.",
    "Variety is measured on a 3-scale depending on the number of dissimilar task components. foot_4",
    "Relationship: Inter-connectedness and interdependencies of the various task components are considered in the relationship dimension.",
    "We measure this by counting the edges in the task-dependency graph."
  ]
